title: For Real at .500, Shaq’s Big Splash, and Khalil Mack’s Revenge | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Robert Mays and Kevin Clark take a look at .500 teams (02:00), Tampa Bay striking gold with Shaq Barrett (13:00), the biggest three games of Week 5 (22:00), and Khalil Mack’s return to Oakland (36:00).
